import { Grid,TextField, Button } from "@material-ui/core";
import { Container, Typography, Paper } from "@material-ui/core";


const Bookingform = () => {

  const getVehiclenumber = (e) => {
      console.log(e.target.value)
  }
  
  const bookedSlot = (e) => {
    console.log(e.target.value)
}
  
  return(
  <Container style={{ padding: 16, margin: "auto", maxWidth: 800 }}>
    <Typography
      variant="h4"
      align="center"
      component="h1"
      style={{ padding: 16 }}
    >
      Parking Lot Management System !
    </Typography>
    <Grid>
      <Paper style={{ padding: 16 }}>
        <Grid container justify="flex-start" alignItems="center" spacing={2}>
          <Grid item xs={12}>
            <TextField
              label="Vehicle Number"
              color="secondary"
              variant="outlined"
              type="Text"
              fullWidth
              onChange={getVehiclenumber}
            />
          </Grid>

          <Grid item xs={12}>
            <TextField
              label="Entry Time"
              color="secondary"
              variant="outlined"
              fullWidth
              type="time"
              defaultValue="00:00:00"
            />
          </Grid>

          <Grid item xs={12} mt={4}>
            <TextField
              label="Exit Time"
              color="secondary"
              variant="outlined"
              fullWidth
              type="time"
              defaultValue="00:00:00"
            />
          </Grid>

          <Grid item xs={12}>
            <TextField
              label="NumberOfSlot"
              color="secondary"
              variant="outlined"
              type="Text"
              fullWidth
              onChange={bookedSlot}
            />
          </Grid>

          <Grid
            container
            justify="space-evenly"
            alignItems="center"
            style={{ padding: 16 }}
          >
            <Button variant="contained" color="primary" type="submit">
              Submit
            </Button>
            <Button variant="contained" color="secondary" type="button">
              Reset
            </Button>
          </Grid>
        </Grid>
      </Paper>
    </Grid>
  </Container>
)};

export default Bookingform;
